Class SimpleQuery

    Provides an example of performing a simple query using the i2b2-Java-API A simple example would be the following: java SimpleQuery i2b2demo demo demouser http://192.168.56.101:9090/i2b2/services/QueryToolService Demo \\\\i2b2_DEMO\\i2b2\\Demographics\\Gender\\
